WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.834
How about it?

00:00:03.337 --> 00:00:05.338
My mother isn't well.

00:00:06.924 --> 00:00:09.008
They're doing some tests.

00:00:09.510 --> 00:00:12.178
That's why I'm going home.

00:00:12.513 --> 00:00:14.639
I'm sorry. I didn't know.

00:00:15.516 --> 00:00:17.600
How could you possibly?

00:00:18.852 --> 00:00:23.815
I hope she feels better,
and if she does, bring her with you.

00:00:27.194 --> 00:00:30.530
Goodbye, Avery. Have a good flight.

